data.description: Want to buy a one of a kind magnificent home?  Then this definitely is the home is for you!  Custom, high-end finishes throughout!  5 bedrooms plus den/office, 5 bathrooms, 3 car garage; one of the larger homes in Sugarmill Woods.  From the pavers drive to the double entry doors, visually relish the 1-1/4" hardwood floors, tray ceilings, den, living and family rooms (with wood burning fireplace), formal dining room and breakfast room.  Exquisite kitchen is a chef's dream with built-in commercial size refrigerator, gas range, built-in double ovens and microwave, and wine refrigerator.  Beautiful granite countertops and island.  Two wood burning fireplaces; one is in the family room and one is in the primary bedroom.  3 bedrooms (including primary suite) are on the main floor; 2 bedrooms and an oversized media room with wall-sized viewing screen, wet bar and adjoining bathroom on the second floor make this an entertainer's paradise.  2nd floor balcony overlooks pavers lanai with concrete pool and separate pond with waterfall feature.  Pool has automatic cleaner, waterfall and spa.  Outdoor shower and kitchen with sink and gas line for grilling enhance the generous size lanai.  Underground propane tank (2005).  Beautiful greenbelt affords privacy to enjoy nature at its finest!  This spectacular home does not disappoint.  Roof 2005 (with documented 5 years of roof life left); 3 HVAC units (2 are 2023 and 1 is 2016).
